d to high mass ratios (q>0.7) are fundamental\nproperties of BDs. Current theories of BD formation do not appear to provide a\ngood description of all these properties.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 17 May 2003 03:33:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-07"}
