sis of the\nsoluble point wavefunction. Finally, we briefly discuss the prospects for\nunderstanding this physics in a wider range of models and for making contact\nwith experiments.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 17 May 2003 01:29:54 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 20 Jun 2003 22:23:52 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 25 Nov 2003 17:40:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2007-05-23"}
